OL,3,CPokemon cards: The growing popularity
OL,4,Cof a children's toy said to outpace
OL,5,Cgold
OL,7,FWords by ITV News Producer Kieran
OL,8,FCarter
OL,10,FThe Pokemon company is celebrating its
OL,11,F30th birthday on Friday. It does so as
OL,12,Fthe world's biggest media franchise,
OL,13,Fwith total revenues of $147 billion
OL,14,F(#110 billion), according to Guinness
OL,15,FWorld Records.
OL,26,@kD@DrrrD@Hrr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/37
