OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772220031
OL,3,CPokemon cards: The growing popularity
OL,4,Cof a children's toy said to outpace
OL,5,Cgold
OL,7,FSpanning games, cartoons, and other
OL,8,Fmerchandise, it is the trading cards -
OL,9,Fonce a children's playground hobby -
OL,10,Fthat now create such fanatic devotion
OL,11,Famong fans, frequently selling for
OL,12,Fthousands of pounds and in some
OL,13,Finstances outpacing gold and
OL,14,Ftraditional stocks as investments.
OL,16,FEarlier this month, the trading cards
OL,17,Fwon the People's Choice Award at the
OL,18,F2026 Toy of the Year Awards, while the
OL,19,FiPhone companion app also holds the
OL,20,Ftitle for iPhone game of the year.
OL,26,@kD@Drr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/37
