OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772220031
OL,3,CPokemon cards: The growing popularity
OL,4,Cof a children's toy said to outpace
OL,5,Cgold
OL,7,FHigh-profile sales of cards for eye-
OL,8,Fwatering amounts, like YouTuber and
OL,9,Fboxer Logan Paul's record auction of a
OL,10,FPikachu card earlier this month for
OL,11,F$16.492 million (#12.178 million),
OL,12,Fcontinue to create headlines, exposing
OL,13,Fthe cards to wider audiences.
OL,15,FBut their rising popularity has also
OL,16,Fseen them become a target for
OL,17,Fcriminals and scalpers hoping to
OL,18,Fprofit from the high demand.
OL,26,@kD@Drr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/37
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772220031
OL,3,CPokemon cards: The growing popularity
OL,4,Cof a children's toy said to outpace
OL,5,Cgold
OL,7,FSo, why are they so popular, and what
OL,8,Fshould collectors watch out for if
OL,9,Fattempting the company's catchphrase
OL,10,Fand hoping to "catch 'em all"? ITV
OL,11,FNews explains.
OL,13,FWhat are they?
OL,15,FPokemon cards, or Pokemon TCG (trading
OL,16,Fcard game), are collectible cards
OL,17,Ffeaturing characters from the Japanese
OL,18,Fanimation and video game.
OL,26,@kD@DrrwD@DrrwD@Vrr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/37
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772220031
OL,3,CPokemon cards: The growing popularity
OL,4,Cof a children's toy said to outpace
OL,5,Cgold
OL,7,FThey are commonly bought in packs of
OL,8,F10, with buyers unaware of the cards
OL,9,Fthat will be in their pack before
OL,10,Fopening.
OL,12,FThe first sets of cards were released
OL,13,Fin Japan in 1996, with an English
OL,14,Fversion not available to the public
OL,15,Funtil 1999.
OL,26,@kD@Drr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/37
