PN,31706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772220031
OL,3,CPokemon cards: The growing popularity
OL,4,Cof a children's toy said to outpace
OL,5,Cgold
OL,7,FThis original English set consisted of
OL,8,F102 cards, or 103 with an alternate
OL,9,Fversion of Pikachu included in some
OL,10,Fsets, compared to the many thousands
OL,11,Fof unique English-language cards that
OL,12,Fnow exist.
OL,14,FCards from this original set
OL,15,Ffrequently sell for thousands of
OL,16,Fdollars in mint condition and have
OL,17,Feven pushed up the price of unopened
OL,18,Ffirst edition packs in the hopes they
OL,19,Fmay contain a rare card.
OL,26,@kD@Drr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/37
