FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772220031
OL,3,CPokemon cards: The growing popularity
OL,4,Cof a children's toy said to outpace
OL,5,Cgold
OL,7,FPrices range widely between different
OL,8,Fcards and also different qualities of
OL,9,Fcards, with Professional Sports
OL,10,FAuthenticator (PSA) existing as an
OL,11,Findependent grading service
OL,12,Fdetermining the quality, and therefore
OL,13,Fprice, of cards based on print defects
OL,14,Fand damage.
OL,16,FAs well as collector items, the cards
OL,17,Fare also used to compete in local and
OL,18,Fglobal tournaments, with people going
OL,19,Fhead-to-head in mock battles,
OL,20,Fattempting to score the most points.
OL,26,@kD@Drr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/37
