PN,31708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772220031
OL,3,CPokemon cards: The growing popularity
OL,4,Cof a children's toy said to outpace
OL,5,Cgold
OL,7,FWhat has happened to their value?
OL,9,FIn 1999, a pack of the original cards
OL,10,Fset UK fans back around #2.50 (#4.85
OL,11,Fwhen adjusted to today's money).
OL,13,FThese days, newer packs sell for
OL,14,Fbetween #8 and #20, whilst an opened
OL,15,Foriginal pack has risen from 1999's
OL,16,Fpocket change to an average of #364,
OL,17,Faccording to price-checking site Price
OL,18,FCharting.
OL,26,@kD@Drr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/37
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772220031
OL,3,CPokemon cards: The growing popularity
OL,4,Cof a children's toy said to outpace
OL,5,Cgold
OL,7,FThe return on investment for some
OL,8,Fcollectors has often been described as
OL,9,Fmore favourable than the average stock
OL,10,Fmarket investment, with data from
OL,11,FThistle Tavern Trading Cards
OL,12,Fhighlighting how some individual cards
OL,13,Fhave outperformed gold over the same
OL,14,Fperiod.
OL,16,FDerrick Hunt, the founder of UK
OL,17,Fauction house Cullens of Surrey
OL,18,FAuctions, said Pokemon cards have
OL,19,F"come a long way" from a time when
OL,20,Fthey were seen as purely a children's
OL,21,Fcollectable or trading game.
OL,26,@kD@DrrzD@Srr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/37
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772220031
OL,3,CPokemon cards: The growing popularity
OL,4,Cof a children's toy said to outpace
OL,5,Cgold
OL,7,F"I remember their release in the UK
OL,8,Faround 1999-2000, when they were
OL,9,Ffirmly aimed at kids," he said.
OL,11,F"Having been heavily involved in the
OL,12,Ftrading card scene for over 10 years,
OL,13,Fand through our work at Cullens of
OL,14,FSurrey Auctions, we've seen a
OL,15,Fsignificant shift in how these items
OL,16,Fare viewed.
OL,26,@kD@Drr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/37
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772220031
OL,3,CPokemon cards: The growing popularity
OL,4,Cof a children's toy said to outpace
OL,5,Cgold
OL,7,F"Certain Pokemon cards have shown
OL,8,Fperformance comparable to, and in some
OL,9,Fcases stronger than, traditional
OL,10,Finvestment assets like stocks, shares,
OL,11,Fand even precious metals.
OL,13,F"They're now often treated more like
OL,14,Fcollectable artworks in their own
OL,15,Fright.
OL,17,F"Since the pandemic in particular,
OL,18,Finterest in the trading card game
OL,19,F(TCG) market has accelerated rapidly,
OL,20,Fand there are no signs of that
OL,21,Fpopularity slowing down," Hunt said.
OL,26,@kD@DrroD@Mrr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/37
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772220031
OL,3,CPokemon cards: The growing popularity
OL,4,Cof a children's toy said to outpace
OL,5,Cgold
OL,7,FCan't view this table on your mobile
OL,8,Fdevice? Click here to open it in
OL,9,Fbrowser.
OL,11,FToy World's John Baulch told ITV News
OL,12,Fthe cards' popularity has endured
OL,13,Fsince they were first released 30
OL,14,Fyears ago.
OL,16,F"For kids, they are a form of
OL,17,F'playground currency' ` they're very
OL,18,Fmuch perceived as a cool thing to
OL,19,Fhave," said Baulch.
OL,26,@kD@Drr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/37
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772220031
OL,3,CPokemon cards: The growing popularity
OL,4,Cof a children's toy said to outpace
OL,5,Cgold
OL,7,F"Of course, many adults who grew up
OL,8,Fwith them are now rediscovering the
OL,9,Fjoy of collecting, while many are
OL,10,Fdelighted to be able to share that joy
OL,11,Fwith their own children.
OL,13,F"We have certainly seen this happen
OL,14,Fwith numerous toy brands and ranges.
OL,15,FConsumers are attached to the toys
OL,16,Fthey remember fondly as kids, and now
OL,17,Fthey have grown up and have more
OL,18,Fdisposable income of their own,
OL,19,Fthey're happy to spend it on something
OL,20,Fwhich brings them joy and evokes fond
OL,21,Fmemories of their own childhood."
OL,26,@kD@Drr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/37
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31714
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772220031
OL,3,CPokemon cards: The growing popularity
OL,4,Cof a children's toy said to outpace
OL,5,Cgold
OL,7,FThe Logan Paul effect
OL,9,FYoutuber and boxer Logan Paul set a
OL,10,Fnew record last week by selling a rare
OL,11,FPokemon card at auction for the
OL,12,Fhighest price ever recorded.
OL,14,FPaul's Pikachu Illustrator card sold
OL,15,Ffor a record $16.492 million (#12.178
OL,16,Fmillion) according to auction firm
OL,17,FGoldin, though this included the
OL,18,Fdiamond necklace to which it was
OL,19,Fattached, one once worn by Paul at a
OL,20,Fwrestling event.
OL,26,@kD@DrrsD@Drr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/37
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31715
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772220031
OL,3,CPokemon cards: The growing popularity
OL,4,Cof a children's toy said to outpace
OL,5,Cgold
OL,7,FThe card, one of just 39 printed in
OL,8,Fthe late 90's, is considered the only
OL,9,Fone in mint condition and had
OL,10,Fpreviously set a record for the most
OL,11,Fexpensive Pokemon card when Paul
OL,12,Fbought it in 2021 for $5.3 million
OL,13,F(#3.9 million).
OL,15,FSpeaking to ITV News' US partner CNN,
OL,16,FGoldin's founder and CEO, Ken Goldin,
OL,17,Fsaid over the past 20 years, the value
OL,18,Fof Pokemon cards had rocketed,
OL,19,Foutpacing similar products and even
OL,20,Fbeating the S&P stock market for
OL,21,Freturn on investment by up to 3,000%.
OL,26,@kD@DrrsD@NrrzD@Grr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/37
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31716
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772220031
OL,3,CPokemon cards: The growing popularity
OL,4,Cof a children's toy said to outpace
OL,5,Cgold
OL,7,F"This is the most coveted trading card
OL,8,Fin the world," he said.
OL,10,FCullens' Hunt said he credits part of
OL,11,Fthe cards' popularity to high-profile
OL,12,Fcollectors such as Logan Paul who,
OL,13,Fthrough social media, has exposed the
OL,14,Fcards to a much wider audience than
OL,15,Fthey may otherwise have reached.
OL,17,FWhy such a large increase?
OL,19,FSeveral factors play into the cards'
OL,20,Frising prices, aside from the brand's
OL,21,Fcontinued popularity.
OL,26,@kD@DrroD@AOUpD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/37
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31717
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772220031
OL,3,CPokemon cards: The growing popularity
OL,4,Cof a children's toy said to outpace
OL,5,Cgold
OL,7,FCullens' Derrick Hunt told ITV News,
OL,8,F"As with most collectables, once
OL,9,Fproducts go out of print, prices can
OL,10,Frise sharply.
OL,12,F"There's often talk of a 'bubble', and
OL,13,Fwhile short-term dips do happen,
OL,14,FPokemon today is very different from
OL,15,Fthe early-2000s boom and crash. It's
OL,16,Fnow a global franchise and, for many
OL,17,Fpeople, a lifestyle. The involvement
OL,18,Fof high-profile buyers and sellers,
OL,19,Fcombined with Pokemon's strong and
OL,20,Fongoing marketing strategy, means it's
OL,21,Funlikely to simply disappear."
OL,26,@kD@DrrvD@Drr{D@Rrr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/37
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31718
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772220031
OL,3,CPokemon cards: The growing popularity
OL,4,Cof a children's toy said to outpace
OL,5,Cgold
OL,7,FUnboxing videos of Pokemon cards
OL,8,Fremain hugely popular on YouTube,
OL,9,Fattracting hundreds of thousands of
OL,10,Fviews as fans hope to draw rare cards
OL,12,FThe difficulty in obtaining the cards
OL,13,Fis another factor driving up their
OL,14,Fprices as fans buy stock hoping to
OL,15,Fpull a rare and expensive artwork.
OL,26,@kD@DrroD@Wrr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/37
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31719
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772220031
OL,3,CPokemon cards: The growing popularity
OL,4,Cof a children's toy said to outpace
OL,5,Cgold
OL,7,FCards are printed in limited runs, and
OL,8,Fcollectors have been known to buy and
OL,9,Fstore multiple copies of some sets,
OL,10,Fincreasing the rarity and artificially
OL,11,Fdriving up the price for sale at a
OL,12,Flater date.
OL,14,FEfforts to combat this have seen some
OL,15,Fsellers limit the amount customers are
OL,16,Fable to buy, with Pokemon's store on
OL,17,FAmazon requiring users to request an
OL,18,Finvite to buy certain sets.
