OL,3,CPokemon cards: The growing popularity
OL,4,Cof a children's toy said to outpace
OL,5,Cgold
OL,7,FToy World's John Baulch said: "While
OL,8,Frare Pokemon cards can sell for huge
OL,9,Fsums ` which inevitably attracts
OL,10,Fscalpers and individuals who just see
OL,11,Fit as an opportunity to cash in `
OL,12,FAsmodee and its retail partners have
OL,13,Fworked extremely hard to make sure
OL,14,Fthat distribution is as fair as
OL,15,Fpossible, and that people can't just
OL,16,Fcome in and buy everything up when it
OL,17,Fis first released.
OL,26,@kD@DrrpD@Irr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G20/37
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31721
SC,0021
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772220031
OL,3,CPokemon cards: The growing popularity
OL,4,Cof a children's toy said to outpace
OL,5,Cgold
OL,7,F"Generally, retailers limit the number
OL,8,Fof sets and packs which can be
OL,9,Fpurchased by any one individual," he
OL,10,Fsaid, adding: "I also know that many
OL,11,Ftoy retailers hold sets back for
OL,12,Fregular customers and families with
OL,13,Fkids, so that everyone gets a fair
OL,14,Fchance and the fanbase continues to
OL,15,Fgrow."
OL,17,FLimited edition events
OL,26,@kD@Drr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G21/37
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31722
SC,0022
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772220031
OL,3,CPokemon cards: The growing popularity
OL,4,Cof a children's toy said to outpace
OL,5,Cgold
OL,7,FOne way the cards' popularity is
OL,8,Fmaintained is through collaborations,
OL,9,Ffrequently featuring limited edition
OL,10,Ftrading cards only obtainable at an
OL,11,Fevent.
OL,13,FIn 2023, Amsterdam's Van Gogh Museum
OL,14,Fcelebrated its 50th anniversary by
OL,15,Fpartnering with Pokemon to display a
OL,16,Fsection of Van Gogh-inspired Pokemon
OL,17,Fart, with a Pikachu card based on the
OL,18,FDutch artist's work available to
OL,19,Fvisitors.
OL,26,@kD@DrrwD@TrrxD@arr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G22/37
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31723
SC,0023
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772220031
OL,3,CPokemon cards: The growing popularity
OL,4,Cof a children's toy said to outpace
OL,5,Cgold
OL,7,FThe promotion saw huge demand for
OL,8,Ftickets, with merchandise and slots
OL,9,Fselling out in days, and the museum
OL,10,Feventually had to withdraw the card
OL,11,Ffrom being offered due to safety
OL,12,Fconcerns over large crowds attending.
OL,14,FIn a statement at the time, the museum
OL,15,Fsaid the promotion had created an
OL,16,F"undesirable situation", claiming the
OL,17,Factions of "a small group of
OL,18,Findividuals" had "led (it) to take the
OL,19,Fdifficult decision to remove the
OL,20,FPikachu with Grey Felt Hat promo card
OL,21,Ffrom the museum."
OL,26,@kD@DrrzD@WpmzD@Zpn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G23/37
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
