CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772220031
OL,3,CPokemon cards: The growing popularity
OL,4,Cof a children's toy said to outpace
OL,5,Cgold
OL,7,FPrice-checking site Price Charting
OL,8,Festimates the average cost of one of
OL,9,Fthese cards is now around $645 (#480),
OL,10,For close to $2,000 (#1,488) in mint
OL,11,Fcondition.
OL,13,FAt the time of the promotion, some of
OL,14,Fthese cards were seen listed for sale
OL,15,Fonline for as much as #7,000, though
OL,16,Fnot necessarily sold for this amount
OL,17,Fat the final bid.
OL,26,@kD@Drr
