OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772220031
OL,3,CPokemon cards: The growing popularity
OL,4,Cof a children's toy said to outpace
OL,5,Cgold
OL,7,FSimilar collaborations have taken
OL,8,Fplace between Pokemon and the Tokyo
OL,9,FMetropolitan Art Museum's "Munch: A
OL,10,FRetrospective" exhibition, as well as
OL,11,FJapan's postal service.
OL,13,FCullens' Derrick Hunt says events like
OL,14,Fthese help "keep the brand culturally
OL,15,Frelevant", as wider audiences are
OL,16,Fexposed to the Japanese company.
OL,18,FIn the UK, previous collaborations,
OL,19,Fincluding limited-edition cards, have
OL,20,Feven taken place at McDonald's.
OL,26,@kD@DrrpD@RrrqD@[OUrD@NO]
