OL,3,CPokemon cards: The growing popularity
OL,4,Cof a children's toy said to outpace
OL,5,Cgold
OL,7,FLondon's Natural History Museum is
OL,8,Fcurrently hosting a pop-up Pokemon tie-
OL,9,Fin with merchandise and an oversized
OL,10,Fpromotional card on offer to all
OL,11,Fvisitors. Tickets for the event sold
OL,12,Fout in less than two hours.
OL,14,FHead of Retail at the Natural History
OL,15,FMuseum Claire Bevan, told ITV News:
OL,16,F"For us, there is a wonderful
OL,17,Falignment between Pokemon and the
OL,18,FNatural History Museum ` we're both
OL,19,Fbig fans of the natural world and its
OL,20,Fevolution and diversity.
OL,26,@kD@DrrpD@_rrxD@AOUyD@Vrr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G26/37
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
