CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772220031
OL,3,CPokemon cards: The growing popularity
OL,4,Cof a children's toy said to outpace
OL,5,Cgold
OL,7,F"We hope that across our audiences,
OL,8,Fthe collaboration will spark joy and
OL,9,Fcuriosity in the creatures around us,
OL,10,Fboth in the world of Pokemon and
OL,11,FEarth."
OL,13,FThe Kabuto King
OL,15,FIt is not just rare cards that have
OL,16,Fseen their prices increase.
OL,26,@kD@DrrrD@YrrsD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G27/37
