OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31730
SC,0030
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772220031
OL,3,CPokemon cards: The growing popularity
OL,4,Cof a children's toy said to outpace
OL,5,Cgold
OL,7,FSome have speculated whether this
OL,8,Fwould even be possible without
OL,9,Fimmediately crashing the average price
OL,10,Fof his collection.
OL,12,FHe has, however, sold at least one
OL,13,FKabuto, a signed copy, which went for
OL,14,Fjust over $50,000, and from which he
OL,15,Fsays all proceeds were donated to St
OL,16,FJude Children's Research Hospital in
OL,17,FTennessee.
OL,19,FOpen to exploitation
OL,26,@kD@Drr
