OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772220031
OL,3,CPokemon cards: The growing popularity
OL,4,Cof a children's toy said to outpace
OL,5,Cgold
OL,7,FThe cards' popularity has led to
OL,8,Fseveral scams as people seek to
OL,9,Fexploit their prices and desirability.
OL,11,FUsually sold in sealed packs, buyers
OL,12,Fsign up to a certain degree of chance
OL,13,Fwhen purchasing a pack, with the
OL,14,Fgamble being part of the "appeal" for
OL,15,Fcollectors.
OL,26,@kD@Drr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G31/37
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31732
SC,0032
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772220031
OL,3,CPokemon cards: The growing popularity
OL,4,Cof a children's toy said to outpace
OL,5,Cgold
OL,7,FSome sellers have resorted to weighing
OL,8,Findividual packs, claiming that
OL,9,Fheavier sets are more likely to
OL,10,Fcontain expensive cards, with the
OL,11,Frarer holographic cards weighing
OL,12,Ffractionally more due to their
OL,13,Fprinting process.
OL,15,FAnother method collectors and sellers
OL,16,Fattempt to cheat the system is by
OL,17,Fscanning unopened packs with a metal
OL,18,Fdetector, typically used in home
OL,19,Fimprovement projects.
OL,26,@kD@Drr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G32/37
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31733
SC,0033
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772220031
OL,3,CPokemon cards: The growing popularity
OL,4,Cof a children's toy said to outpace
OL,5,Cgold
OL,7,FThough not a foolproof method, videos
OL,8,Fonline show that in some sets, the
OL,9,Fmetal detector can reliably predict
OL,10,Fwhether a pack contains a rare card
OL,11,Fbased on the materials used to print
OL,12,Fit.
OL,14,FThis leaves buyers purchasing
OL,15,Findividual packs open to the
OL,16,Fpossibility that it may have already
OL,17,Fbeen scanned by a seller to determine
OL,18,Fwhether it contained an expensive card
OL,19,F- greatly reducing the chance of
OL,20,Fnaturally finding a rare one.
OL,26,@kD@Drr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G33/37
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31734
SC,0034
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772220031
OL,3,CPokemon cards: The growing popularity
OL,4,Cof a children's toy said to outpace
OL,5,Cgold
OL,7,FThe rising demand for Pokemon cards,
OL,8,Fmatched by the soaring prices, has
OL,9,Fmade them a prime target for theft as
OL,10,Fwell.
OL,12,FRecent months have seen multiple
OL,13,Freports from gaming shops claiming
OL,14,Fthey have been targeted by thieves
OL,15,Flooking to steal packs of cards in
OL,16,Fbulk for an easy profit.
OL,18,FJuliano Scibelli told ITV News Anglia
OL,19,Fhe estimated nearly #100,000 of stock
OL,20,Fhad been stolen from his shop in
OL,21,FPeterborough last month
OL,26,@kD@DrroD@Zrr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G34/37
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31735
SC,0035
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772220031
OL,3,CPokemon cards: The growing popularity
OL,4,Cof a children's toy said to outpace
OL,5,Cgold
OL,7,F"There's a stigma that it's just
OL,8,Fcards, but it really isn't. It's a
OL,9,Flife for most people now," he said.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FAs Pokemon celebrates its birthday,
OL,17,Fevents and collaborations are expected
OL,18,Fto take place around the world
OL,19,Fthroughout the rest of the year.
OL,26,@kD@DrrxD@Grr
