OL,3,CPokemon cards: The growing popularity
OL,4,Cof a children's toy said to outpace
OL,5,Cgold
OL,7,FThese officially began with a one-
OL,8,Fminute trailer at the US Super Bowl
OL,9,Ffeaturing celebrities like Lady Gaga,
OL,10,Fwhich some estimated may have cost
OL,11,Fmore than the total budget for the
OL,12,Fmost recent Pokemon video game.
OL,26,@kD@DrrtD@Prr
