OL,3,CPokemon cards: The growing popularity
OL,4,Cof a children's toy said to outpace
OL,5,Cgold
OL,7,FIn a statement, President of The
OL,8,FPokemon Company International, Kenji
OL,9,FOkubo, said: "The Pokemon community
OL,10,Fhas been the foundation and
OL,11,Finspiration for the brand since the
OL,12,Fvery beginning, and the passion of our
OL,13,Ffans is what has allowed Pokemon to
OL,14,Fhave a lasting impact on pop culture
OL,15,Faround the world and across
OL,16,Fgenerations."
